[assistant]     "The unsafe-access properties are tied to Java 25/native-image current-defaults behavior and should still be validated by the authoritative Gradle native test.",
[assistant]     "Avoid depending on internet endpoints; local in-process HTTP coverage is enough for normal WebClient request, response, multipart, redirect, cookie, and caching paths."
